<category>
	<pattern>I enjoy managing IT systems and ensuring smooth operations </pattern>
	<template>Excellent choice! Given your interests, a role like Systems Manager would be a great fit for you. A Systems Manager oversees IT infrastructure, ensures network security, and manages a team to keep systems running efficiently. To get started, develop skills in IT management, cloud computing, cybersecurity, and system administration using tools like AWS, Windows Server, and Linux.</template>
